<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>DCCA One-Stop Career Centers</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#800080" ALINK="#800080">


<img src="../../graph/oscc/sietc2.jpg" width=175 height=129 align=left>
<hr>
<h2 align=center>What is an Illinois Employment & Training Center (IETC)?</h2>

An IETC (formerly known as a One-Stop Career Center) is an office where the public can easily access a broad array of employment, training and related services.  One or more IETCs will be located in each of Illinois' 26 service delivery areas designated under the Job Training Partnership Act (JTPA).  Some services will be available through satellite offices and through computer technology in areas of the state where location of an IETC is not practical.<p>


<hr>
<strong>| <a href="../../home.htm"> DCCA Home</a> | <a href="ietc.htm"> IETC</a> |</strong>


</body></html>
</DOC>
