<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>DCCA One-Stop Career Centers</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#800080" ALINK="#800080">


<img src="../../graph/oscc/sietc2.jpg" width=175 height=129 align=left>
<hr>
<h2 align=center>What services will be available to students and schools?</h2>

IETCs will be a source of the latest labor market information (LMI) for schools, libraries and students.  LMI products will be available on-site and will be distributed by the IETC in hard copy and via computer (e.g., distribution of software and LANs).  IETCs will also be a source of in-service training for career counseling personnel regarding the use of LMI products.  Students and dropouts may also use the IETC to obtain career counseling and to learn about "second chance" education programs.<p>

<hr>
