<DOCNO>WT11-B09-101</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000234-B029-195</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://ilcommerce.com:80/dcca/files/business/export3.htm 206.30.252.18 19970108000431 text/html 3674
