<h2>Illinois Department of Commerce & Community Affairs</h2>
<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogo.gif" alt="First Stop Business Information Center" width=334 height=160>
<br clear=all>
<IMG SRC="/dcca/graph/fs/fsbar.gif">
</center>
<br clear=all>
<p>
<h4>
Welcome to the <a href="../files/fs/other/fsinfo.htm"> First Stop Business Information Center</a>!<p>

Whether you're looking for help with <a href="../files/fs/other/fsguide.htm"> starting a business</a> or trying to determine what <a href="fsbr.htm"> government requirements or permits</a> apply to your business, First Stop is your information source. And, if you can't find what you're looking for, First Stop offers you <a href="fsasst.htm"> personal assistance</a>.<p>

Give First Stop a try and <a href="mailto:first.stop@accessil.com">let us know</a> how we're doing. We need your feedback and suggestions to help us serve you better.<p>

Thank you for making us your First Stop for information and assistance!<p>

<em>Dennis R. Whetstone, Director</em><p>
</h4>
<center><img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fsbar.gif"></center>
<p>
<center>
<img src="../Graph/FS/ToSearchGovt.GIF" alt="To Search Government Information for Business" width=338 height=45><p>
<a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/menus/fsap.htm"> <img src="/dcca/graph/fs/Profiles.gif" alt="Agency Profiles" border=0></a>
<a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/menus/fsbr.htm"> <img src="/dcca/graph/fs/Reqment.gif" alt="Requirements" border=0></a>
<a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/menus/fsba.htm"> <img src="/dcca/graph/fs/Assistance.gif" alt="Assistance" border=0></a>
<p>
<center><img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fsbar.gif"></center>
<p>
<a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/menus/fssearch.htm"> <img src="../Graph/FS/SearchAllFiles.JPG" alt="Search All Files" width=263 height=36 border=0></a>
</center>

<h4 align=center>
<hr>

