<html><head>
<title>Rock Valley College Information</title></head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">
<img src="http://www.ilcommerce.com/graph/logosm.jpg" alt="DCCA Logo" width=165 height=82 align=left>
<img src="http://www.ilcommerce.com/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<h3>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs<p></h3>
<img src="http://www.ilcommerce.com/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4>
<img src="http://www.ilcommerce.com/graph/sbdc3.gif" alt="SBDC Logo" width=200 height=160 align=right>
<p>
<center><h1>Rock Valley College</h1></center><hr>
<strong>Rock Valley College</strong><br>3301 N Mulford Road / Room 262<br>Rockford, IL 61114-5640<p>Phone: (815) 654-5524<br>Fax: (815) 654-5524<hr>
<h2>Services Offered</h2><dl>
<p><dt><strong>General Business Management Services</strong><dd>SBDC:  As a Small Business Development Center, this organization provides businesses with a wide range of general business management services.  They can assist you with the development of your business plan.  They can help you define your marketing objectives and approaches.  They work with you to improve your business ownership skills and show you how to analyze your business finances.  The SBDC will also help you access other specialized services such as export assistance or government marketing expertise and information.<p>For more information contact Beverley Kingsley at (815) 654-5524.
<p><dt><strong>Government Procurement Assistance</strong><dd>PTAC:  This organization provides specialized services to Illinois businesses that want to do business with government at any level - local, state or federal.  As a Procurement Technical Assistance Center, they will provide general counseling in government procurement practices to help you sell your products or services.  They will help you identify government markets.  They can show you where to access bid specifications and help you review bid packages.  They can also provide information about contract administration and other contracting assistance services.<p>For more information contact John DiGiancomo(815) 654-5524.
</dl><hr>
<strong>| <a href="/DCCA/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</a> | <a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/menus/ilsb.htm"> Big Help for Small Business</a> |</strong>
</body></html>
</DOC>
