<head>
<title>Illinois Business Assistance Resource Service</title>
</head>
<body BackGround="/DCCA/graph/back.gif" text="#000080" link="#000080" vlink="#800080" alink="#800080">
<img src="/DCCA/Graph/SmallLogo.gif" align=left>
<img src="/DCCA/Graph/SBDC.gif" align=right>
<br clear=all>
<hr>
<center><img src=/DCCA/Graph/BusAsstLogo.gif></center>
<strong><p>This service is provided by the Department of Commerce and Community Affairs to help you do business better.
<hr>
<p>Select the type of service or information you need from the list below:
<ul>
<p><li>Locating <a href="/DCCA/Menus/BusinessAssistance/SBDCNet.htm">business assistance services</a> from organizations with offices near you.
<p><li><a href="/Temp/IETC.htm">Employer services</a> from an Illinois Employment Training Center in your area.
<p><li><a href="/DCCA/Menus/fsm1.htm">Government requirements and assistance.</a>
<p><li>Business location services online:
<ul>
<p><li>Infrastructure information for <a href="http://www.accessil.com/DCCA/Menus/CommunityProfiles/Home.htm">Illinois Communities.</a>
<p><li><a href="bldgsite.htm">Buildings and sites</a> available for your business startup or expansion.
<p><li><a href="/Temp/IlDemo.htm">Illinois Demographics</a>: markets and labor information.
<p><li>Let us <a href="contact.htm">contact</a> you.
</ul>
<p><li>Participate in online services to:
<ul>
<p><li>Network with others in the <a href="exchange.htm">Illinois Business Exchange.</a>
<p><li>Join <a href="maillist.htm">mailing lists</a> for government and industry announcements.
<p><li><a href="busreg.htm">Register your business</a> for special services.
<p><li>Illinois government procurement needs.
</ul>
<p><li>Locate <a href="directry.htm">business associations</a> to help grow your business.
</ul>
</strong>
