<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Small Business Incubator Map</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">


<img src="/dcca/graph/logosm.jpg" alt="DCCA Logo" width=165 height=82 align=left>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<h3>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs<p></h3>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4>

<img src="../../graph/sbdc3.gif" alt="SBDC Logo" width=200 height=160 align=right>

<h2>Small Business Incubators</h2>
<hr>
<strong>
<h3><a href="#Location Directory">Location Directory</a></h3>

The Illinois Small Business Incubator Program helped establish a network of 20 incubators throughout the state. These incubators provide prospective business owners with inexpensive space to lease, shared secretarial and administrative resources, and management support to small business tenants. Having helped hundreds of businesses get started, the incubators range from technology-specific to general use and offer an important and useful opportunity to start-up and early-stage companies.<p>

<a name="Location Directory"><hr></a>
<a href="/Progs/IMap32.exe/IncubatorRegions"><img src="/DCCA/Graph/BusAsstRegions.gif" alt="Region Map, see below" border=0 ismap align=left></a>
<p>Click on a region in the map at the left to get more information about Small Business Incubators in that region.
<br clear=all>
<hr>
<p>We also have a text only version:
<p><a href="/Progs/BusAsstMain.exe?AsstProgPageType=RegionalOfficeList&ProvType=50&Region=1">Northwestern Illinois</a>
<br><a href="/Progs/BusAsstMain.exe?AsstProgPageType=RegionalOfficeList&ProvType=50&Region=2">Northeastern Illinois, Chicago Collar Counties</a>
<br><a href="/Progs/BusAsstMain.exe?AsstProgPageType=RegionalOfficeList&ProvType=50&Region=3">Cook County, Illinois, Chicago</a>
<br><a href="/Progs/BusAsstMain.exe?AsstProgPageType=RegionalOfficeList&ProvType=50&Region=4">Eastern Illinois</a>
<br><a href="/Progs/BusAsstMain.exe?AsstProgPageType=RegionalOfficeList&ProvType=50&Region=5">Central Illinois</a>
<br><a href="/Progs/BusAsstMain.exe?AsstProgPageType=RegionalOfficeList&ProvType=50&Region=6">Southeastern Illinois</a>
<br><a href="/Progs/BusAsstMain.exe?AsstProgPageType=RegionalOfficeList&ProvType=50&Region=7">Southwestern Illinois</a>
<br><a href="/Progs/BusAsstMain.exe?AsstProgPageType=RegionalOfficeList&ProvType=50&Region=8">Western Illinois</a>
</strong>

