<h3>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs<p></h3>
<img src="http://www.ilcommerce.com/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4>
<img src="http://www.ilcommerce.com/graph/sbdc3.gif" alt="SBDC Logo" width=200 height=160 align=right>
<p>
<center><h1>Richard J. Daley College</h1></center><hr>
<strong>Richard J. Daley College</strong><br>7500 South Pulaski Road / Building 200<br>Chicago, IL 60652<p>Phone: (773) 838-0319<br>Fax: (773) 838-0303<hr>
<h2>Services Offered</h2><dl>
<p><dt><strong>Technology Research Awards</strong><dd>SBIR:  As a Small Business Innovative Research Center, this organization can help you compete for Federal research and development awards in technology intense fields.  They will provide counseling, training and technical assistance to business entrepenuers working in this area for the purpose of promoting the formation, growth and development of small innovative firms.  The focus of the assistance is on what awards may be available and how can you get the contracts.<p>For more information contact Jim Charney at (773) 838-0319.
