<h3>
Department of Commerce & Community Affairs<p>
</h3>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<font size=+2>Small Business Environmental Assistance Program</font>
<br clear=right>
<hr>

<center>
                     <h2>ENVIRONMENTAL SERVICES DIRECTORY</h2>
<h4>           Illinois Department of Commerce and Community Affairs<br>
              Small Business Environmental Assistance Program</h4>
                        620 East Adams, Third Floor<br>
                       Springfield, Illinois  62701<p>

    For more information please contact Amelia Gooding at 217/785-4557.<p>
</center>
<strong>Special Notice: </strong> The Department of Commerce and Community Affairs, Small
Business Environmental Assistance Program provides the Environmental
Services Directory as a general informational/educational service for
Illinois small businesses.  All inquiries regarding a listing should be
directed to that business by phone or mail.  Any Illinois business
providing environmental related services to commercial or industrial end
users will be considered for inclusion in the Directory.  For additional
information call 217/785-4557.<p>

<b>   THIS INFORMATION DOES NOT CONSTITUTE AN ENDORSEMENT OF ANY BUSINESS,
                     SERVICE, WARRANTY OR INDIVIDUAL.</b>

<hr>
