completing 5-8th grades!!!  
</h4>
You can still sign up for Camp KEEP, July 14-19, 1996. Camp KEEP (Kids for Energy and Environmental Protection) is a week long energy/environmental camp held at a camp site just northwest of Springfield in Cantrall, IL. Come join us for a fun-filled week of learning about energy and the environment in a camp setting with swimming, boating, hiking and  outdoor activities. Invite a friend!!! Send in the attached reservation form NOW! For detailed information, call Peggy Chamness at 217/785-3411; TDD, 217/785-0211.<p>

